                                FlexJobs work from home jobs site was created in 2007 to provide a trusted, more effective, friendly, 
                                and overall better way to find professional, remote, and flexible jobs.

                                <br> <br>

                                We were founded by job space pioneer Sara Sutton after she had been looking for a flexible job 
                                after starting her family. She realized that millions of others were just as frustrated by the ads, scams, 
                                and inefficiencies on other job boards that wasted her time in finding a good, flexible job, so she decided to create the solution she was looking for.

                                
                                <br><br>
                                
                                It wasn’t our original intention, but somehow <span class="text-primary">FlexJobs has become a leader in the flexible job movement</span> that's currently disrupting the traditional workforce. 
                                We seem to show up in the press weekly as people turn to us for guidance. 
                                You can browse hundreds of those articles on our Press page.   hand-screens every job listing to ensure legitimacy, saving you time and protecting you from scams.
                                
